    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>We estimated mean serial interval and superspreading potential for the predominant Delta variant of SARS-CoV-2. Mean serial intervals were similar with 3.7 and 3.5 days during early and latter periods, respectively. Furthermore, the risk of superspreading events was similar with 23% and 25% of cases seeded 80% of all transmissions.</jats:p>",
